### Eureka Server checks
### Scope: registry and service discovery visibility

@eurekaBase = http://localhost:8761

### 1) Eureka UI reachable (expect 200)
GET {{eurekaBase}}
Accept: text/html

###
### 2) All registered apps (expect 200)
GET {{eurekaBase}}/eureka/apps
Accept: application/json

###
### 3) Auth service registration (expect 200 when auth-service is running)
GET {{eurekaBase}}/eureka/apps/AUTH-SERVICE
Accept: application/json

###
### 4) API Gateway registration (expect 200 when gateway is running)
GET {{eurekaBase}}/eureka/apps/API-GATEWAY
Accept: application/json

###
### 5) Quantity service registration (expect 200 when quantity-service is running)
GET {{eurekaBase}}/eureka/apps/QUANTITY-SERVICE
Accept: application/json

